    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S is a masterclass in analog precision and mechanical integrity. At its heart lies the naturally aspirated 3.6L flat-six, featuring VarioCam Plus for an optimized torque curve and seamless power delivery. The G96 six-speed manual transaxle provides tactile, short-throw engagement, distributing power through a sophisticated all-wheel-drive system that ensures neutral handling and immense lateral grip. This example boasts a pristine chassis with original Bilstein suspension components and four-piston monobloc Brembo calipers over cross-drilled rotors. Exhaustive preventative maintenance has been performed, including a dual-row IMS bearing upgrade and a new rear main seal, ensuring the M96 powerplant remains leak-free and robust. The wide-body aerodynamic profile is flawless, with factory paint depth consistency and a spotless undercarriage, representing a turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
